{
  "stem": "20978.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had such a good life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard about it, as a kid of course, in Lithuania and Poland it started much earlier than it did in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we heard that the Jews are being deported, and the train was coming through Debrecen, through the city, I volunteered with other young boys.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took a basket, and we collected food from the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we met the train to give it to the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I could never imagine that that would happen in a city-- in a country where I was born, where we lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because life was so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those days, my father was home yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Nazis, well, I heard it in shul, most of the things you hear, you know, like they used to say, [NON-ENGLISH], you know, I heard it being said.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to listen to the Voice of America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it came a time when Jews were not allowed to have radios, like you couldn't employ any Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to listen to it in a basement, the Voice of America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, you know, in secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I would-- they would send me out in a yard to make sure nobody is coming, you know, nobody comes in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how we got-- we got the news what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And until one day I remember we were planning our Purim play in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans raided Debrecen, you know, the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, like the day before, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after that things just went bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, only what we saw on the street, you know, the-- the Hungarian newspaper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some, not not all of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
